<paragraph blockId="58.[151,1058,445,497]" pageId="58" pageNumber="1017">
E t y m o l o g y: The trivial name, 
<emphasis box="[539,602,445,466]" italics="true" pageId="58" pageNumber="1017">sentus</emphasis>
, is a Latin name with a meaning of &quot;rough&quot;; with reference to the very rough surface on the pronotal disc.
</paragraph>
